    <item>
      <title>六名众议院民主党人投票谴责哈里斯的边境政策</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/six-house-democrats-vote-to-condemn-harris-on-border-policies</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周四，六名摇摆选区的众议院民主党人与共和党人一起投票谴责副总统卡马拉·哈里斯的政府打击非法移民的表现。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/six-house-democrats-vote-to-condemn-harris-on-border-policies</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 15:24:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国支持加拿大填补中国电动汽车“漏洞”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/us-backs-canada-moving-to-close-chinese-electric-car-loophole</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国驻加拿大大使表示，有迹象表明贾斯汀·特鲁多总理领导的政府正在堵塞“漏洞”，这一漏洞可能允许中国支持的电动汽车通过加拿大进入美国，从而避开关税，这令他感到鼓舞。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/us-backs-canada-moving-to-close-chinese-electric-car-loophole</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 15:01:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Meta 将在市场斗争中受到欧盟反垄断命令的打击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/meta-set-to-be-hit-by-eu-antitrust-order-in-marketplace-fight</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Meta Platforms Inc. 因被控将 Facebook Marketplace 与其社交网络捆绑在一起，滥用其在分类广告市场的主导地位，面临欧盟的首次罚款。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/meta-set-to-be-hit-by-eu-antitrust-order-in-marketplace-fight</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 14:52:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>胡塞武装袭击致俄罗斯商品在红海不安全</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/russian-commodities-aren-t-safe-in-red-sea-as-houthis-attack</link>
      <description><![CDATA[也门胡塞武装袭击的运载俄罗斯商品的商船数量，比袭击世界其他任何地方产品的商船都要多，凸显出今年早些时候胡塞武装向莫斯科提供的安全通行保证的局限性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/russian-commodities-aren-t-safe-in-red-sea-as-houthis-attack</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 14:33:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>克罗地亚禁止三名黑山官员进入欧盟，令欧盟之路更加复杂</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/croatia-bans-three-montenegro-officials-complicating-eu-path</link>
      <description><![CDATA[克罗地亚禁止三名黑山政客入境，理由是他们涉嫌损害这两个巴尔干邻国之间的关系，这一争端可能会影响黑山加入欧盟的进程。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/croatia-bans-three-montenegro-officials-complicating-eu-path</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 14:07:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>勒梅尔称法国政治僵局正在损害经济</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/france-s-political-impasse-is-harming-the-economy-le-maire-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国看守财政部长警告称，由于总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙犹豫是否任命新总理，经济正在受到打击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/france-s-political-impasse-is-harming-the-economy-le-maire-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 14:02:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>肯尼亚收到阿达尼投资其最大机场的提案</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/kenya-receives-adani-proposal-to-invest-in-its-biggest-airport</link>
      <description><![CDATA[肯尼亚机场管理局表示，肯尼亚政府收到了阿达尼机场控股有限公司投资该国主要机场的提议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/kenya-receives-adani-proposal-to-invest-in-its-biggest-airport</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 13:02:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普对哈里斯的攻击可能让他失去他需要的选民</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/trump-risks-losing-voters-he-needs-with-loaded-attacks-on-harris</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普的竞选团队正在疯狂地调整其策略，放弃了将前对手乔·拜登描述为软弱的毫无意义的计划，并对比共和党候选人年轻二十岁的卡玛拉·哈里斯测试新的攻击路线。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/trump-risks-losing-voters-he-needs-with-loaded-attacks-on-harris</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 12:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普选择万斯是一个警告，并购不会轻易通过</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/trump-s-vp-pick-may-signal-that-he-won-t-make-m-a-great-again</link>
      <description><![CDATA[前总统唐纳德·特朗普选择 JD Vance 作为他的竞选搭档，这可能预示着他的第二任期对商业而言可能远不如企业交易员所希望的那样友好。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/trump-s-vp-pick-may-signal-that-he-won-t-make-m-a-great-again</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 19:46:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
